'''Arrif''' d tamnaḍt di ugafa n [[Merruk|Umerruk]], tessajja ɣef [[Ilel Agrakal|Yilel Agrakal]], zeddɣen deg-s gar 3 ar 5 imelyan n imezdaɣ.

Tamurt n Arrif llan deg-s idurar, izaɣaren, d yiftisen xef [[Ilel Agrakal|Yilel Agrakal]]. Idurar d tmurt n Arrif ssenta seg [[Ixef n Sbartil]] (Cape Spartel) d [[Tanja]] deg utaram ar [[Ixef Ikebdanen]] (Ras Kebdana) d [[Asif Amelwi|yiɣzer Amelwi]] (Meřwect) deg wegmuḍ, zeg Ilel Agrakal di ugafa ar [[Iɣẓer n Werɣa]] deg wanẓul.

Seg iɣerman imeqqranen i yellan di temnaḍt n Arrif Ameqqran ɣer-neɣ: [[Nnaḍur]], [[Lḥusima]], [[Tanja]], [[Tiṭṭawin]], [[Accawen]], [[Berkan]], [[Taza]], [[Targist]], [[Azɣenɣan]], [[Seřwan]], [[Miḍar]], [[Zayyu]], [[Aεarwi]], [[Eddriwec]], [[Ayt Buεeyyac]], [[Imzuren]], [[Leεrayec]], [[Ajdir]], [[Tawrirt]], [[Fnideq]], d [[Eljebha]].

Idurar n Arif udsen idurar n “Cordillera Bética” di Sbanya. Idurar n Arif udsen maca ur qqinen ɣer idurar n Watlas. Gar-asen tella [[Taza(Merruk)|Taza]].
Maci marra imezdaɣ n temnaḍt n Arif Ameqqran ssawalen tutlayt Tamaziɣt. Imezdaɣ n Tanja d Tiṭṭawin qqaren i yiɣef-nsen “Jbala” ([[Ijebliyen]]) nitni ssawalen Taɛrabt [[Tajeblit]]. Tamnaḍt n “Jbala” d tafult si temnaḍt n Arrif Ameqqran. Iwdan yessawalen Tmaziɣt di Arif qqaren i yixef nsen “[[Imaziɣen]]” niɣ “Irifiyen”, tutlayt nsen qqaren as lebda “Tamaziɣt” maci "Tarifit". Iwdan n berra i Arif d nitni 

